    <comment>- update to 0.9.9:
  * Infrastructure updates
  * General improvements and modernization of code
  * Allow dash '-' as placeholder in controlled vocabulary lists
  * Fix CTYPE parsing for WCS with SIP distortion extensions
  * Validate nested attribute values using specs
  * Add iteration support for AVM objects
  * Added support for MetadataVersion 1.0
  * Add changelog entries to CHANGES.md on release</comment>
